<<> Blackknight: The ship is okay, Phanna. Now come on, we'll go check 
> other parts of the ship to see if we can find anyone. Meggy can even 
> help us!>>

Phanna grinned wide, cuddling her little plushie more so "Okey-day!" The ship 
wasn't hurt too bad then...that was good. Everybody'd be fine, and they'd all 
just get right back up and go on with the trip! Hopefully all the toys in her 
room were alright...
